msgid "Print multiple features for each map if they meet the criteria"
msgstr "यदि प्रत्येक मानचित्र मानदंडों को पूरा करता है तो उसके लिए अनेक सुविधाएँ प्रिंट करें"

msgid "For JSON, this places features under a \"features\" key"
msgstr "For JSON, this places features under a \\\"features\\\" key"

